    <div class="col-md-6">
        <p> Basti already saw that I was not doing well and sent me directly into the bungalow when we were back on land. There was a cool shower and a round of dozing in bed. After almost 1.5 hours I was finally available again and we wanted to go back to Alona. But then we met the two girls again and decided to spontaneously eat together in the resort restaurant. Then there were evil-delicious hamburgers, drowned in garlic for me. Basti had chicken meat with vegetables and potato slices. During the meal we talked about the plans for the next few days. For the girls it should go to Oslob tomorrow to go swimming with whale sharks and Basti planned to go diving one last time tomorrow morning. Afterwards there may be an exploration of the neighboring towns on our note. </p>
        <p> We also considered what we could do on Friday. The idea was to charter a boat and drive out another round to start a last attempt to see turtles. The two girls then told that they were already on Balicasag and that it was very nice and that one literally falls over the turtles. We asked at the reception and there we were told that it was not a problem that there would be a private boat and the costs were 1800 PHP (approx. 30 &euro;) including 2 companions, plus 250php (approx. &euro; 4.50) per nose. Cool! The girls have already announced interest. We decided to wait until the girls are back from their trip to Oslob. </p>
